{"tid":2287923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李健仁感謝古仔甘比幫忙","createTime":"2020-11-16T06:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T08:02:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad9af8cf6cc457f65aabced60b8a61a01851c76","tid":2287923,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201116/BMUM2WHFCNCZBPEWTZFSHJFGXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201116%2FBMUM2WHFCNCZBPEWTZFSHJFGXA%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3kB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=8731e9e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201116%2FBMUM2WHFCNCZBPEWTZFSHJFGXA%2F&h=3a3b2775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201116/BMUM2WHFCNCZBPEWTZFSHJFGXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李健仁感謝古仔甘比幫忙<br />\n<br />\n李健仁因早年在周星馳電影中飾演「如花」而為觀眾熟悉，去年在深圳焗桑拿時中風，導致半邊身癱瘓及不能說話。近月他慢慢康復，昨日在社交平台留言感謝大家幫忙：「我想在此感謝這半年來出錢出力幫助我的有心人，首先多謝劉鑾雄太太（甘比），在我出事返港後，即派同事聯絡我，另外還有演藝人協會會長古天樂，劉太及古生兩位大善人出錢出力。」<br />\n<br />\n田啟文（田雞）昨接受《蘋果》訪問，談及好友李健仁的康復進展：「。。。。。。。。。。。。」另外，醫生向親友透露余慕蓮肺部好轉，她一直清醒，醫生亦建議拔喉，但會在她的頸部開一小口來插喉，如情況穩定，下周便做這個小手術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VIryeyUcejag7OF2l2HlupTz2E0=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AEZ45NB6XNAU7K5B543JM7OFVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVIryeyUcejag7OF2l2HlupTz2E0%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAEZ45NB6XNAU7K5B543JM7OFVI.jpg&h=abd09aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李健仁（左）去年中風，慢慢康復的他昨日貼出近照。 微博圖片"},{"pid":"d2014b5934f077d31a81061b908f094a4fffabb9","tid":2287923,"uid":134119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad9af8cf6cc457f65aabced60b8a61a01851c76","tid":2287923,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislik